{
  "stem": "1938.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were eating the snow on the way to-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When it came to night, they put us in a, a stable from, from the cows and not let--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was warm.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And not let-- not all the time-- not let us in to see there was machines.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We fell on, on on the points machines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One or the other screaming, was all languages-- Hungarian, and, and, and it was just terrible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "March.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was all ours.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was all your people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were Hungarians there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The last-- the last, the last few months, they brought some Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But all the time was just the Polish neighborhood, like Bedzin, Sosnowiec, Katowice, and all them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every day was less and less.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they want to finish up that they can be free from, from their duties.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But somehow, they, they shoot a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had one time, I couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My feet were swollen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I decide, whatever will be.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I saw-- I'm petite.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I can fit in a doghouse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the, in the light, in the morning, I decide I will run out to this doghouse.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and, and when he catch me, of course, he can shoot me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So as a petite, I went into this doghouse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden I see the, the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a tall guy, SS man, with a small, a this small golden gun.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was shooting everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when I saw him coming, I said shema yisrael, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said to me, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He couldn't believe it, what I did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why did you run out in, in the light, in the daytime?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
